                    <comment id="12633560" author="hossman" created="Tue, 23 Sep 2008 00:33:47 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed revision 698035.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;it&apos;s just about having an optional ant property for specifying the full path to svnversion ... i&apos;ve made the Hudson config changes for Lucene-trunk (add -Dsvnversion.exe=/opt/subversion-current/bin/svnversion) and manually kicked off build#594.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If i missed something, re-open and i&apos;ll take a look&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                    <comment id="12633563" author="mikemccand" created="Tue, 23 Sep 2008 00:36:45 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Super thanks Hoss!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
